Steve Jobs;;73;;85;;R;;With public anticipation running high, Apple Inc. co-founders Steve Jobs (Michael Fassbender) and Steve "Woz" Wozniak get ready to unveil the first Macintosh in 1984. Jobs must also deal with personal issues related to ex-girlfriend Chrisann Brennan and their young daughter Lisa. Eventually fired, Jobs launches NeXT Inc. and prepares to release a new computer model in 1988. Ten years later, Jobs is back at Apple Inc. and about to revolutionize the industry once again with the iMac.;;Drama,Biography;;Danny Boyle;;2015;;Michael Fassbender,Kate Winslet,Seth Rogen,Jeff Daniels,Michael Stuhlbarg,Katherine Waterston,John Ortiz,Sarah Snook,Adam Shapiro,Makenzie Moss,Ripley Sobo,Perla Haney-Jardine;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/steve_jobs_2015